config BR2_PACKAGE_IOEXAMPLE1
    bool "Example: LED control with c-periphery"
    help
      This package provides an example C application that demonstrates
      controlling an LED named "led-red" using the c-periphery library.

      The application allows interactive control over the LED state via
      standard input. The user can turn the LED ON or OFF or quit the
      application by entering 1, 0, or q respectively.

      This example uses:
        https://github.com/vsergeev/c-periphery